Merlino</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 05, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=28023\">Limiting Quiescent Search Depth</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Merlino</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 20, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=28620\">Potentially Trapped Pieces</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Merlino</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 24, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Trapped_Pieces\" title=\"Trapped Pieces\">Trapped Pieces</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30333\">Return eval or upper bound?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Merlino</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 26, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a>, <a href=\"/Fail-Hard\" title=\"Fail-Hard\">Fail-Hard</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30738\">Only recaptures in qsearch?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Merlino</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 21, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31220\">Stupid Extension Problem/Question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Merlino</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 23, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><sp